  "texts": [
    "Table 3 presents the top 10 authors and their corresponding article metrics.",
    "Wang F.Y. from the Institute of Automation Chinese Academy of Sciences in China stands out with the highest article count of 9 and a total of 23 citations.",
    "Following closely is Wu H. from Duke University School of Medicine in the USA, with seven articles and 16 citations.",
    "Interestingly, Kleebayoon A. from Joseph Ayo Babalola University in Nigeria and Wiwanitkit V. from Chandigarh University in India have published 6 articles each but have not received any citations.",
    "On the other hand, authors with a lower article count have also garnered significant citation numbers."
  ]
}